            "title": "John Pike - ศิลปินสีน้ำแห่งบอสตัน",
            "summary": "John Pike - ศิลปินสีน้ำแห่งบอสตัน อีกหนึ่งศิลปินสีน้ำในดวงใจ&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1e1gfi1i70\" class=\"align-center\"><strong>John Pike - ศิลปินสีน้ำแห่งบอสตัน</strong></h2>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1535309623569-OJ2FGWGD9K4BKSF6RSDV/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kEbaKfLOXq9aV_Na11-JLSR7gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z5QPOohDIaIeljMHgDF5CVlOqpeNLcJ80NK65_fV7S1UUo5wkIPnUxQlIOasByD_rbVFYJc2ZZRCHDLsw6OZlvrIHxqS7YzfUzKVWbOQ6Gvaw/John+%26+Zellah+1936.JPG?format=1000w\" width=\"672\" height=\"529\"></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">อีกหนึ่งศิลปินสีน้ำในดวงใจ ที่ผมชื่นชอบมากๆ และเป็นอีกหนึ่งศิลปินที่ผมศึกษาผลงานของเค้า</p>\n<p><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1541786429703-BF8MH5UWTY0MIPNSCEUG/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kNbqRjjH4ZCG-uxCiu8ARj9Zw-zPPgdn4jUwVcJE1ZvWQUxwkmyExglNqGp0IvTJZUJFbgE-7XRK3dMEBRBhUpz9zQDsXxlD7hn8iQtarJu02bSZbtgQRyd1a1prDhm8X1PmRithAwwuu9W0Vr3BGx8/Universal+Regular.jpg?format=500w\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"452\"></p>\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\n<p class=\"align-center\">นอกเหนือจากการเขียนรูป John Pike ยังเป็นผู้แต่งหนังสือสีน้ำที่ขายดีมากๆสองเล่มและยังคิดค้นจานสีและ perspective finder ที่เป็น Signature ของตนเองอีกด้วยครับ</p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"> </p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1535304971438-TC5FYNJIV325ZFRGJ9V0/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kO6y_8hb1Sl1k6TNq-ueXOl7gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z5QHyNOqBUUEtDDsRWrJLTmnhbJtrfwp8bfXu9iW6TjnzTY57WGFV7jDnrDfT5NBSM9E8Z1iTdHOqievDIQakP9/Australian+Shepherds.jpg?format=1500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1530889454409-7TZ37NWO7SW7AFXA0MQ9/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kEtDbO_Y_eoWH0YCEp57CINZw-zPPgdn4jUwVcJE1ZvWQUxwkmyExglNqGp0IvTJZamWLI2zvYWH8K3-s_4yszcp2ryTI0HqTOaaUohrI8PIqbHfhXr2FvDPuCrt3WhYUK013O50wfnsRAJ7la2kCtkKMshLAGzx4R3EDFOm1kBS/Archway.JPG?format=1000w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1530889483186-T6NYXF5PNOBO5H8CI5JY/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kCp2XA3QfgssHohi3vhVLJEUqsxRUqqbr1mOJYKfIPR7LoDQ9mXPOjoJoqy81S2I8N_N4V1vUb5AoIIIbLZhVYy7Mythp_T-mtop-vrsUOmeInPi9iDjx9w8K4ZfjXt2dnLPUQ15mTRkf3Roq76t3R-pWpKGzC4OeiLcYnxAoDO9JvwGh1qtNWvMhYKnvaKhbA/Blowing+Snow.jpg?format=2500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1535304693693-WKM0M5IUU60UJDVF61MM/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kL9NlD64Zl1_YNsxHZzrt5IUqsxRUqqbr1mOJYKfIPR7LoDQ9mXPOjoJoqy81S2I8N_N4V1vUb5AoIIIbLZhVYxCRW4BPu10St3TBAUQYVKczgQTLgOc95pyYDyyONvWHyhfmcWRZ_62ep69UaJUUgpe_NQiaMmEwaw9NV3fLciG/Blessed+are+the+Merciful.jpg?format=1500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p class=\"align-center\">ผลงานของ John Pike มักจะมีสีสันที่สดใส และมีกลิ่นอายออกแนวอารมณ์การ์ตูนนิดๆ แต่ก็ยังมีแสงเงาที่สวยงามมากๆ</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1530889648996-61FC5FVPR9RMF3X2CXJV/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kFPg9sTnll0gJ9DpzQ9PJAUUqsxRUqqbr1mOJYKfIPR7LoDQ9mXPOjoJoqy81S2I8N_N4V1vUb5AoIIIbLZhVYxCRW4BPu10St3TBAUQYVKcVqNGKPVzELKU-qvyGnoY7beW-3IHZN6bUab3ZRCsQKmE1CWROD_BDG6aY4k_Dy2t/Busy+Farm.JPG?format=1500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1535305116984-MMH3JQ34M4XK7184V9HZ/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kG1IWMiKR-1-iLqz89yQncx7gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z5QPOohDIaIeljMHgDF5CVlOqpeNLcJ80NK65_fV7S1UTa1eUVVylpramfcORFkw7WJrCBq3zBSYhfYiIxyjXO6j4iYTpAzo2Ukj9cdZWGPAg/Cabin+on+the+Hill.JPG?format=2500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1549479476238-DJQ05EASLXWT6KRX0GK0/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kF2gAsBYBqvDbADHI-zmH1QUqsxRUqqbr1mOJYKfIPR7LoDQ9mXPOjoJoqy81S2I8N_N4V1vUb5AoIIIbLZhVYxCRW4BPu10St3TBAUQYVKcVcWEUSVM53emzuCACZrn-XKdEtQe3t77JT6uXCCWFEjd1-6rzLPQTbkXyjJn8jwK/Camping.jpg?format=1500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1530889708269-FIZMRC0E376MMQGSJEWT/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kPKrCSbcZGlnTD4GzrjFG9Z7gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z4YTzHvnKhyp6Da-NYroOW3ZGjoBKy3azqku80C789l0hHMyhIh2kKzuOL3ydJCryAGkbRUsM0qN0JDfN7-a7UjBp8b2CK8n_BCx0XjYOth-w/card2.JPG?format=2500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1530889906886-PIPFKQR77LSB1Q5DL292/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kEAqygFSJxB2hz9a7YtTOkZ7gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z5QHyNOqBUUEtDDsRWrJLTmQyViSO8WVy1F2YAzXWvEVE2rkRozMLhT1LBqspLaO87uZ_44DG7-kd--lRQnPeHM/DSCN0034.JPG?format=1500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1535304234308-INPTQHRRFD1QIK3K6NWU/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kMrm8coVyX_7js3ML3s62RN7gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z5QHyNOqBUUEtDDsRWrJLTmmbLecD_NwfjqNxjfNDWHyK6Mr9MsWZD0PzASHWqHiQ-6aQRYQMH5mJmVm9KYFhRm/DSCN0037.JPG?format=1500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>John Pike ยังได้รับรางวัลต่างๆมากมาย อาทิ </p>\n<ul>\n<li>American Watercolor Society Award, the National Hallgarten Prize</li>\n<li>Salmagundi Black and White Prizes</li>\n<li>A.W.S. Watercolor U.S.A. Award</li>\n<li>1974 recipient of the National Academy Walter Briggs Memorial Award</li>\n<li>1976 top National Academy Watercolor Award William A. Patton Prize</li>\n<li>A.W.S. John Young Hunter Award</li>\n<li>The Academic Artists Association Helen Gould Kennedy Award</li>\n<li>Franklin Mint Gold Medal Award</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1535304099740-ORSSWC2IHRM5MINJESQ0/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kM7fgWnvnnH7ROJnlCofmMF7gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z5QPOohDIaIeljMHgDF5CVlOqpeNLcJ80NK65_fV7S1UeT4-Q0GRtGZzsiqDt15z0haKUHONKJv_RHIXPLN6fYNLIXfY3DEqu8fc08UsQJ-4w/Chow+Hound+Taos.JPG?format=2500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1535304258007-HR9UACIF5NHUZ9W0TO6H/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kL0Ej2urPjl6hUCOTJi2q9p7gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z5QPOohDIaIeljMHgDF5CVlOqpeNLcJ80NK65_fV7S1UV5hkIZ0kEv90DyxXng0tfHsJrh_-84EjuAMCz6fsWOl7nJgZEpy_9PHS0K1tm4k-g/DSCN0040.JPG?format=2500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1535304276178-WOWKSL69ON0HBGVFEXW3/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kFo-bqFVzUxoJrv5y_IwM_97gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z5QHyNOqBUUEtDDsRWrJLTmi7D7yXkH8nfwsxTs5kW9h0EVHazzbAg3UyL4tyF2r2jZe4WhaAxymWbnKRzSewh3/DSCN0042.JPG?format=1500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1535304299027-8GM16367XBR2XHN2NE3Q/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kFBd9TcvPXXaUjA4z11_W8B7gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z5QPOohDIaIeljMHgDF5CVlOqpeNLcJ80NK65_fV7S1USzCmGCRJtum1ry1dIxCaILuByZuresWFsj-elLT-Dtuy4esdQB3BRl8sZrbGldWOw/DSCN0043.JPG?format=2500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1530889997261-OZK6ZV85SNQ72C8N7A19/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kGqjzssiOWPPSWLv0IS2VFd7gQa3H78H3Y0txjaiv_0fDoOvxcdMmMKkDsyUqMSsMWxHk725yiiHCCLfrh8O1z5QHyNOqBUUEtDDsRWrJLTmzZHn3PYdZUow1T0ZeZQrhdraz7-0DC_tAW_eriryGOi9JiUyqlSii_cPXrJbo5hF/DSCN0045.JPG?format=1500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5a88b96290bade54a7863543/1535304615127-TDU6LDUU0OLU414T6TVZ/ke17ZwdGBToddI8pDm48kHKxRuxYtOF8X_W7X3t9f9wUqsxRUqqbr1mOJYKfIPR7LoDQ9mXPOjoJoqy81S2I8N_N4V1vUb5AoIIIbLZhVYxCRW4BPu10St3TBAUQYVKci4hDdjxmqXGkp_vr5yO-R028prWeJ3Huz9g1L5aRraH8GWJO82m3bAd5GlEVa7ut/Fritzi+and+Fred.jpg?format=1500w\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\"></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><img class=\"post__image--left\" src=\"https://www.johnpikeart.com/john-pike-art-works/h43z28qltu9tpdjeb6trsc6wjzegl0\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">พี่น้องคนใหนอยาก ดูงานเพิ่มเติมของศิลปินท่านนี้</p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">สามารถเข้าไปชมได้ที่</p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.johnpikeart.com/john-pike-art-works/\">https://www.johnpikeart.com/john-pike-art-works/</a></p>\n<hr>\n<p class=\"align-center\">มาเขียนสีน้ำกันครับ</p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/buk.chainuwat/\">Buk Chainuwat</a> - บุ๊ค ชัยนุวัตร</strong></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><img class=\"post__image--center\" src=\"https://chainuwat.github.io/media/posts/24/WEBSITE-LOGO.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"262\" height=\"100\"></p>\n</div>",
